Recommended

if you want her to look exactly like she does in the screenshots you will have to download: 
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] [size=3][b]and overwrite the [/b][/size][size=4]Ningheim[/size][size=3][b] files located in:[/b] [/size][size=2]C:\Users\[/size][b]Username[/b][size=2]\Documents\Mod Organizer\mods\The Ningheim Race\textures\actors\character\Ningheim\female[/size]
[size=2] [/size]
